quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Ta-seen-meem"
  26,2,"Tilka ayatu alkitabialmubeen"
  26,3,"LaAAallaka bakhiAAun nafsaka allayakoonoo mu/mineen"
  26,4,"In nasha/ nunazzil AAalayhim mina assama-iayatan fathallat aAAnaquhum lahakhadiAAeen"
  26,5,"Wama ya/teehim min thikrin minaarrahmani muhdathin illa kanooAAanhu muAArideen"
  26,6,"Faqad kaththaboo fasaya/teehim anbaoma kanoo bihi yastahzi-oon"
  26,7,"Awa lam yaraw ila al-ardi kamanbatna feeha min kulli zawjin kareem"
  26,8,"Inna fee thalika laayatan wamakana aktharuhum mu/mineen"
  26,9,"Wa-inna rabbaka lahuwa alAAazeezu arraheem"
  26,10,"Wa-ith nada rabbukamoosa ani i/ti alqawma aththalimeen"